| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0822 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c74296d9-dfc7-5d72-a22e-e47c9c92f8bd"
